data.description: This three bedroom, two full bath home is located two blocks from the levee in Pontchatrain Shores. Open floor plan, along with built in Canadian red oak wood bookshelves and cherry nutmeg solid doors throughout the house. With a custom built bar and plenty of room for a pool table, this house is built to entertain! NEWER double insulated windows, 3-ton a/c unit, and 50 gallon water heater, which are all under two years old. Conveniently located minutes from East Jefferson Hospital, Lakeside Shopping Mall, gourmet restaurants, and I-10. Come make this home your own! MOTIVATED SELLER!! BRING ALL OFFERS!!
